<div class='media__message'>
<h4 class='h12 talk-link__speaker'>Mary Bassett</h4>
<h4 class='h9 m5'>
<a class='' href='http://www.ted.com/talks/2445?language=en' lang='en'>
Why your doctor should care about social justice
</a>
</h4>
<div class='meta'>
<span class='meta__item'>
Posted
<span class='meta__val'>
Feb 2016
</span>
</span>
<span class='meta__row'>
Rated
<span class='meta__val'>
Informative, Inspiring
</span>
</span>
